# Mobile Product Principles

- Student Help is Android-first and mobile-first.
- Student experience is the top priority.
- Admin and vendor screens should still be usable on mobile.
- Prioritize demo stability and user safety.
- Demo screens must feel populated and realistic.
- Do not add realtime GPS, payment, delivery tracking, or real order management.
- Food ordering is manual through chat.
- AI features are optional and must not block core app use.

